things for the guitar to do,

40:04.960 --> 40:08.160
so, over time, I started to
amass solo material.

40:09.360 --> 40:13.320
God forgive me, guys, but I just
thought it's the only way to

40:13.320 --> 40:18.080
go to get ideas across is to just
negotiate with myself in the end.

40:18.080 --> 40:20.720
